article.headline: TCU 80, St. Gregory's 38
article.story: FORT WORTH, Texas -- Zvonko Buljan scored 16 points and TCU clobbered winless St. Gregory's 80-38 on Saturday night. Ronnie Moss added 10 points, and Kevin Butler and Jason Ebie grabbed six rebounds apiece for the Horned Frogs (4-3). Josh Coulter had 15 points for St. Gregory's and finished 6-of-6 from the field. But TCU made more shots in the first half (15) than St. Gregory's did the entire game (14). The Cavaliers committed 25 turnovers, leading to 36 points for the Horned Frogs. TCU also had 21 assists to St. Gregory's nine.
